Description of incident: "On March 25, 2016, CertifiKid discovered malicious software code that was inserted by unknown individuals into the server of its e-commerce website between the dates of January 25, 2016 and March 19, 2016."The information compromised included names, credit card numbers, expiration dates and security code information. More Information: http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-61677
